<plot>In a secluded farmhouse, a triangle unfolds involving a powerful and dominant father, his spineless son and obedient daughter. It all happens the day the son is finally determined to make good on his promise to leave everything behind him, following his dream of living in the city. This move brings the triangle to its dramatic climax and to a point of no return.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?231119</url></doc>
